        <br />
        <i style="font-size:18px;color:gray" class="fa fa-thumbs-up pointer">Like</i>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
